data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!! Welcome to 427 Walnut Street. Newly remodeled Victorian home full of charm and character in the heart of Lockport. Outside you'll find it aesthetically pleasing with a freshly painted exterior, new driveway, wrap-around front porch, and original French opening front door. Upon entering the foyer you'll notice the beautiful grand staircase with a stained-glass window. This home features over 2700 sqft of living space with loads of character. Spacious rooms and large windows with plenty of natural light. This home offers a living room, dining room, and bonus room with an updated full bath. Through the pocket doors is the updated kitchen where all the appliances stay & features Granite countertop and soft-close cherry cabinets. Off the kitchen is a large mudroom/1st floor laundry & access to the full basement. You will also find a second back staircase. On the second floor are 4 bedrooms, a Bonus storage room at the end of the hall, and another updated full bath. There are also stairs leading to the full walk-up attic. Updates include roof 2018 HWT 2018 furnace system 2018. New flooring, upstairs/downstairs, and paint, interior/exterior.
